<doc id="146765" wikidata="Q5265719" url="?curid=146765" title="Deterrence">
<text>Deterrence may refer to:

* Deterrence theory, a theory of war, especially regarding nuclear weapons
* Deterrence (penology), a theory of justice
* Deterrence (psychology), a psychological theory
* &quot;Deterrence&quot; (film), a 1999 drama starring Kevin Pollak, depicting fictional events about nuclear brinkmanship</text><links>
